list_percentage_gorgan=[]
list_age_groups=[]
for i in df['age_group']:
    list_percentage_gorgan.append(round(df[df['age_group']==i].p_active_emp.sum()/df[df['age_group']==i].p_total.sum()*100,3))
    list_age_groups.append(i)
    if i == '65+':
        break
list_percentage_gorgan

list_percentage_gorgan_rural_men=[]
list_percentage_gorgan_rural_women=[]
list_age_groups=[]
for i in range(len(df['age_group'])):
    if df.gender.iloc[i]=='':
        list_percentage_gorgan_rural_men.append(round(df[df['settlement']==''][df[df['settlement']=='']['age_group']==df['age_group'][i]].p_active_emp.sum()/df[df['settlement']==''][df[df['settlement']=='']['age_group']==df['age_group'][i]].p_total.sum()*100,3))
        
    
    elif df.gender.iloc[i]=='':
        list_percentage_gorgan_rural_women.append(round(df[df['settlement']==''][df[df['settlement']=='']['age_group']==df['age_group'][i]].p_active_emp.sum()/df[df['settlement']==''][df[df['settlement']=='']['age_group']==df['age_group'][i]].p_total.sum()*100,3))
        
    list_age_groups.append(df['age_group'][i])    
    if df['age_group'][i] == '65+':
        break
list_percentage_gorgan_rural_men

def order(DF):
    temp_cols=DF.columns.tolist()
    new_cols=[temp_cols[-1]]
    new_cols=new_cols+(temp_cols[0:-1])
    DF=DF[new_cols]
    return DF

In [49]:
def ordered_sheets(Adress):
    L=[]
    sheets=pd.ExcelFile(Adress).sheet_names
    for j in range(len(sheets)):
        DF1=(pd.read_excel(Adress,sheet_name=sheets[j]))
        if j==0:
            DF1=DF1.drop(list(range(0,19)),axis=0)
            DF1=DF1.drop([31],axis=0)
        else:
            DF1=DF1.drop(list(range(0,18)),axis=0)
            DF1=DF1.drop([30],axis=0) 
            
        DF1['gender']=1
        DF1['gender'][0:12]=''
        DF1['gender'][12:]=''
        DF1=DF1.drop(columns=['Unnamed: 8','Unnamed: 1','Unnamed: 2','Unnamed: 5'])
        DF1=order(DF1)
        DF1['county_id']=sheets[j][::-1][0:4][::-1]
        DF1['county_name']=sheets[j][::-1][4:][::-1]
        L.append(DF1)
    DF1=pd.concat(L)
    return DF1

def hist_chart(name , x , num_bins):
    plt.hist(x , bins=num_bins,range=(0,1))
    name1 = (name.split('_'))[1]
    name1 += ' emp_ratio'
    plt.title((name1 + ' chart'))
    plt.xlabel(str(name1))
    plt.ylabel('count')
    plt.show()
